b'We asked artists around the world what #KindnessStartsWith. Here\xe2\x80\x99s what London illustrator @nikkimiles_ had to say: \xe2\x80\x9cKindness starts with loving yourself. I have chosen to say this because I believe that self love gives people the optimism and energy to share kindness with others.\xe2\x80\x9d #WorldKindnessDay'

b'We\xe2\x80\x99re partnering with artists from all over to learn more about what #KindnessStartsWith. \xe2\x80\x9cBeing empathetic is the knowledge that we all are imperfect human-beings\xe2\x80\xa6 and sometimes we need someone to remind us we\xe2\x80\x99re not alone. Kindness is taking that empathetic knowledge and acting on it.\xe2\x80\x99\xe2\x80\x9d \xe2\x80\x94 @jacquelinewhitney_, writer #WorldKindnessDay'
